🌐 The main bridge contract;
🗳️ Governance contract for Aleph Zero's bridge decisions;
⛽ Contract to inform guardians about Ethereum gas prices;
🪙 PSP22 token implementation for bridge-created tokens. 

Ethereum contracts include:

🌉 Main bridge contract;
🗳️ Governance contract for Ethereum's bridge decisions;
🧪 Wrapped Ethereum for testing;
🪙 ERC20 token for testing;
🔄 A relayer for bridging the chains.

Note: Some infrastructure code remains private for security. 🔒

MOST is designed for simple and efficient interoperability between Aleph Zero and Ethereum. It's a guardian-based bridge, where each guardian maintains Testnet and Mainnet setups, ensuring sufficient decentralization. 🛡️

